metadata.description: This Emerald Digital Key is 1 of 5000 and gives the Owner a Lifetime Membership in D8A DAO. Perks of this Membership include perpetual monthly rewards, ownership of a Virtual Suite in Our Unreal 5 Metaverse, access to P2E games, and the opportunity to participate in the development of sustainable projects and products. The Most Exciting Feature of this Digital Key is the ability to UNLOCK Treasure from virtual and real world quests with prizes starting at $20,000USD and a Grand Prize worth more than 4 million! Unlock your Destiny! Join D8A DAO today!
metadata.name: Emerald DAO Membership #1
